{"tid":1676040,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"【話你知點解】青衣新樓明翹匯點解平過同區舊樓？","createTime":"2019-10-26T08:02:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-02T14:55:01.000Z","uid":191462,"like":42,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"02193ae24e4f4d5278484ecc3973c3f903eeaced","tid":1676040,"uid":191462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T08:02:56.000Z","msg":"3大原因<br />\n<br />\n1）保養問題<br />\n<br />\n佢本身係斜坡嚟，而加剷平咗一部份嚟起樓。<br />\n將來嗰個斜坡大小事務，都由明翹匯負責維修。<br />\n8年前，嗰個山頭曾經發生過山火。同而家佢個位置相距200米範圍之內。<a href=\"http://archive.am730.com.hk/article-55582\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Farchive.am730.com.hk%2Farticle-55582&d=udS8qETdHRHoQIkzJVaZjgDrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=90df3aa0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://archive.am730.com.hk/article-55582</a><br />\n所以可想言之嗰個地段環境係比較高風險容易出意外，而且保養起上嚟都好麻煩。<br />\n<br />\n2）交通問題<br />\n<br />\n其實嗰個位置嘅交通，出市區得一架葵芳小巴、一架荃灣巴士同一架去青衣城嘅巴士。返工時段同放工時段，係多人到仆街。因為除咗嗰度嘅居民之外，仲有好多青衣IVE嘅學生要用。<br />\n<br />\n3）風水問題<br />\n<br />\n呢個原因應該係住喺附近嘅居民或者學生先會知道。<br />\n佢嗰個山頭其實係有一大片墳墓喺度，對到正一正，分分鐘住高層嘅人係可以好清楚咁望晒。清明重陽有時啲原居民都會上去燒炮仗拜山。<br />\n當年2011年嘅山火發生咗之後，燒咗好多高嘅樹。所以喺青衣IVE都可以望到好清楚成個墳頭。（特別係有啲山泥傾瀉咁嗰個）<br />\n而山上面，除咗普通墳頭外。如果有上過去行山嘅人，可能都見過有啲無名無姓嘅骨塔喺山邊。應該都係以前啲原居民嘅，話晒好多年前青衣都曾經住咗好多水上人，所以夜晚望山其實係好恐怖。<br />\n咁呢個住宅發展嘅時候，有冇郁過人哋乜嘢風水我就真係唔知。但係你諗下夜麻麻望過去，分分鐘連人哋瞓喺度條友叫咩名都望到，你想唔想住真係睇個人興趣。"},{"pid":"2f502e802c80cf1d86696dc619b47b24bf3df6d9","tid":1676040,"uid":191462,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T08:05:44.000Z","msg":"要買呢棟樓嘅ching自己小心。"},{"pid":"c57e8a430279f35889c226c73d1b62cdaa3ddb51","tid":1676040,"uid":191462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T08:08:05.000Z","msg":"利申：喺青衣住咗20幾年"},{"pid":"0ecf660edd5b1215bb53a1bb9ab2b073c8d40c8e","tid":1676040,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T08:08:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5c39eba03a3c9f600d8abbf0b03d9a68ce17b4b","tid":1676040,"uid":122318,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T08:11:18.000Z","msg":"風水問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2df5b49692b0e90961aa397b5514c77bd51676d0","tid":1676040,"uid":38109,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T08:12:28.000Z","msg":"香港邊個地方冇墳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58ee5177221a28f8613852948a445128be97d24c","tid":1676040,"uid":62167,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T08:14:13.000Z","msg":"交通可以改善<br />\n土木工程處修築令冇咩力 唔死人就得"},{"pid":"e9cebcb45df2a9e35b3273fb899f18b1ee1a80e6","tid":1676040,"uid":191462,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c5c39eba03a3c9f600d8abbf0b03d9a68ce17b4b","tid":1676040,"uid":122318,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T08:11:18.000Z","msg":"風水問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T08:14:22.000Z","msg":"我相信連黑警都唔怕嘅連登仔，風水鬼神算得係乜嘢。兜口兜面見到都夠膽直行直過。"},{"pid":"a1b5a971f903e4b0ca5d1e1ee9128552e7a6a809","tid":1676040,"uid":68896,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T08:14:25.000Z","msg":"AA 將全面進場"},{"pid":"a331b102265962d0b548bdcc821cbafa843718c4","tid":1676040,"uid":10014,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T08:14:49.000Z","msg":"邊度有平過，d地產代理同盈翠同灝景比緊係平過，但呢個盤只可以同美景同藍澄灣比"},{"pid":"3a1a03e823ac9177ce67a739bc3db19176a647ff","tid":1676040,"uid":191462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2df5b49692b0e90961aa397b5514c77bd51676d0","tid":1676040,"uid":38109,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T08:12:28.000Z","msg":"香港邊個地方冇墳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T08:15:53.000Z","msg":"其實都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9aecd91cb97965d16669629ae19b22db8797c0ff","tid":1676040,"uid":133502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T08:16:36.000Z","msg":"好唔方便 不了"},{"pid":"1311f280bb9d3c187fc2aafeb14571d06f1964de","tid":1676040,"uid":221813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T08:16:58.000Z","msg":"步行唔到去黨鐵"},{"pid":"1ac59dc27c8133993f7b7aea6c94cb505b578092","tid":1676040,"uid":191462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"58ee5177221a28f8613852948a445128be97d24c","tid":1676040,"uid":62167,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T08:14:13.000Z","msg":"交通可以改善<br />\n土木工程處修築令冇咩力 唔死人就得"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T08:19:19.000Z","msg":"細山路啲路太窄，改善極有限。有車都入唔到，唔好唔記得藍澄灣隔嚟起梗綠置居，又會多一堆人。"},{"pid":"d677015a97a8f4daf410ade674c44557a52c5245","tid":1676040,"uid":191462,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"1311f280bb9d3c187fc2aafeb14571d06f1964de","tid":1676040,"uid":221813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T08:16:58.000Z","msg":"步行唔到去黨鐵"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T08:19:43.000Z","msg":"快嘅30分鐘行到嘅..."},{"pid":"04827d7cc9cc9420a0e83a25657c45f2e03a6bbe","tid":1676040,"uid":66590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T08:22:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲有黑廁 開放廚。"},{"pid":"7854720c1692a00b1579d21b17fc2ae22030af8e","tid":1676040,"uid":61423,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T08:23:57.000Z","msg":"超級唔方便 除左IVE同大陸團酒店就乜都無 出入又孤島咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b098917c185102264cb0f01f6e8058eb15def0d","tid":1676040